# 言犀 · Yanxi

🎯 A LoRA-finetuned Large Language Model project focused on creating emotionally aware, character-consistent AI companions.

🧠 项目目标：训练一个具备个性化人格、语言风格与情绪响应能力的大型语言模型，并探索 prompt 工程与语料微调在“人格塑造”方向的最佳实践。

---

## 🔍 Project Highlights | 项目亮点

- 💬 **Persona Alignment**: Shaped through dialogue-style datasets and emotional prompt structures.
- 🧵 **LoRA Fine-tuning**: Parameter-efficient training using [PEFT](https://github.com/huggingface/peft).
- 🧠 **Custom Instruction Tuning**: Tailored for dialogue context, consistency, and expressive variance.
- 📚 **Bilingual Prompting**: Supports both English and Chinese instruction modes.

---

## 📁 Structure | 项目结构
/dataset/            # Instruction-based training data (Alpaca-style, zh)
├── alpaca_data_zh_51k.json
/model/              # Base model & LoRA adapter output
/scripts/            # Training & inference scripts (PEFT + Transformers)
/Yanxi_App.py        # Gradio-based dialogue interface for testing


---

## 🧪 Current Use Case | 当前应用场景

> A lightweight dialogue interface (Gradio) for testing response coherence, emotional variance, and persona retention.

你可以与“言犀”实时互动，并观察其在情绪表达、人格一致性与 prompt 响应方面的表现。

---

## 🧭 Future Directions | 后续计划

- 🔧 Evaluate multi-turn consistency and long-term memory handling
- 🎭 Explore “persona-switching” via prompt-based control
- 🌐 Host on Hugging Face Space (or deploy via API)
- 📈 Collect feedback for personality fine-tuning (RLHF-style loop)

